Version 0.1
====================================

1. Prepared rails 4.0.4 project with HAML as default template engine, Devise
as autentification layer and Mongoid as database engine.
2. Added Ticket, TicketStatus, Department scaffolds.
3. Added TicketEvent model.
4. Realized validation for Ticket fields(only presense).
5. Realized reference and url for Ticket
6. Realized adding TicketEvents to Ticket.
7. Realized setting of default status to first of TicketStatuses.
8. Enabled auth for all pages excluding ticket add.
9. Fixed all auth troubles in rspec tests.
